{"tid":1469993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚比機管局玩9一日嘅海外巴絲打","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:49:07.000Z","uid":56925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76023d1d60e87ec9127fcb417bf194147ca1c338","tid":1469993,"uid":56925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"屌 完全比機管局玩尻咗<br />\n<br />\n本身琴晚係高雄坐KA飛返香港<br />\n但琴日朝早先被通知班機取消左啦<br />\n再被口頭安排（三日後）16/8先有機返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但最最最仆街嘅係<br />\n*機管局*只係話要重新編排航班升降<br />\n而令到航空公司寫唔到原因同出唔到取消航空證明書<br />\n<br />\n如果想claim翻保險 都要通知書<br />\n所以當我地問cx有無得出證明書既時候<br />\n佢地既回應係 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「宜家出唔到正式文件<br />\n因為我地都諗唔到寫咩原因落文件度」</span></span><br />\n <br />\n到最後黃昏領隊去左機場<br />\n話係DUE TO air traffic flow control而取消 <br />\n但呢個字眼係claim唔到保險架 <br />\n要係airport close，或者public assembly先有機會claim <br />\n<br />\n真係屌佢 <br />\n明明手足就唔撚影響運作 <br />\n但就要取消曬所有航班 <br />\n擺明係想大家覺得呢鋪係因為我地令機場癱瘓<br />\n又唔俾旅客claim到保險 對我地反感<br />\n<br />\n又想玩插禍呀宜家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩依家有大機過咗去 今日可以返到黎<br />\n我係機場等大家接我機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0359c0640e15a164e67e069247539b3500f523e3","tid":1469993,"uid":56925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsTOxsm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsTOxsm.jpg&h=3b0c6341&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a49ff8bc833a4ee508d26bdd395829d29117ac6","tid":1469993,"uid":297518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"612 721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e623a131e81bc24f5f40dce005d1686b1b85e6a","tid":1469993,"uid":297299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n<br />\n一切問題都係機管局，唔關示威者事！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292426575768b674a29ec4f8658a4ca3fc81a7b3","tid":1469993,"uid":298167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"機管局同政府擺明做 show 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966e6fc1d8a6ce4e139da4b3a0a362d91966788e","tid":1469993,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"國泰真係好仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}